                    "numoutlets": 0,
                    "patching_rect": [ 1058.0, 12.0, 445.0, 181.0 ],
                    "text": "Load a pre-analyzed concat corpus into all the required components.\n\nDataset for nearest neighbor matching as well as the audio loaded into a buffer.\n\nThe rate from dk.concatanalysis~ can be passed in to adjust the grain staggering in the matching.\n\n@neighbors = the number of neighbors to return\n@radius = the maximum distance that a returned point can be\n@glitch = likelihood of repeating last grain\n@active = enables or disables the matching\n\nAlso takes onset detection attributes when refering a buffer directly."
                }
            },
